nodes.bodyText: Can you add this change in the changelog
Why is service version getting removed in this PR

It happens to TA as well. "Unless there is a use case, for now lets leave these getServiceVersion calls out."
https://apiview.dev/Assemblies/Review/05d0102010704cfa977f9386ce622294/067d8625611f4b329856ba69b7774d8d

Unclear how Java usually does these docstrings, but I notice in the docstring for the SyncPoller / PollerFlux you don't mention what the poller returns. Python includes this information in the docstring (ex here).
This comment isn't super related to what this PR is trying to do, so feel free to open another PR when / if you want to make this change
Would it also be best to change the forEach for formPage, formTable, formTableCell etc into a for loop as well?
Updated formPage, formTable to loop over an indexed loop but for others the index isn't used in the sample so left as is.
since you're changing the name of layoutPageResults -> contentPageResults, I think it's a good idea to change recognizeLayoutPoller -> recognizeContentPoller
{@link } could be a better option. Usually, use {@code } for the variable name.
